  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some were waiting-- waiting for you to move out of this house and to grab whatever is left over, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at that time, just the beginning of start getting together the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they [INAUDIBLE] we start putting the star of David and start taking Greek Jews, make them into couples to put a big [? band ?] to start gathering-- they had a system how to do it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but we were greenhorns, so-- As we were living at the-- this big apartment there-- for a while, we were-- we were there almost-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] I would say until the beginning of '43, '43.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and middle of '42, they didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they started-- started making different groups, like the [INAUDIBLE] ghettos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They started taking, first of all, sections from north, where were the-- the poor Jews, you [? know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Over ?] there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They started concentrating those, bringing them into a ghetto-- like, same group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
